response.about: Who am I? Well, good question... Let's say I spent 21 years old trying to survive and seeking bliss, and at least I managed to get one of the two things. My name is Ivan, but some friends call me "Emo", I guess because of my hairstyle...I'm NOT emo anyway, just wanted to make that clear. I'm nothing more than a boy who tries to have fun and enjoys hanging out with friends, listening to music, playing/watching football [I used to be lazy and prefer the second one, but Fra recently brought back my passion for the first one], sleeping and doing nothing whenever he can... Some say I take nothing seriously [which in fact isn't always true], because I always try to look happy and make people laugh. It's difficult, I know, and in fact I don't always manage to do it...but if I don't, people seem to worry about that. O_o You know what? I don't care. That's MY lifestyle. That's the reason why I describe myself as a modern Jester, the one who "has" to be happy, and whose aim is to entertain the others. But there's something more behind the mask...
